<p />
<h1><a name="Berkeley_Storage_Manager"></a> Berkeley Storage Manager </h1>
<p />
BeStMan, or Berkeley Storage Manager, is a full implementation of SRM v2.2, developed by Lawrence Berkeley National Laboratory, for a disk based storage and mass storage systems. End users may have their own personal BeStMan that manages and gives an SRM interface to their own local disks. It works on top of existing disk-based unix file systems, and has been reported so far to work on file systems such as NFS, GPFS, PVFS, GFS, Ibrix, HFS+, Hadoop, XrootdFS and Lustre. It also works with any existing file transfer service, such as gsiftp, http, https, bbftp and ftp. It requires minimal administrative efforts on the deployment and updates. BeStMan2 is a Jetty based implementation of SRM v2.2, as opposed to globus container based implementation in the previous BeStMan.
<p />
<h2 class="twikinetRoundedAttachments"><span class="twikinetHeader"><a name="Planning"></a> Planning </span></h2>
<p /> <ul>
<li> <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/BestmanStorageElement" class="twikiLink">BestmanStorageElement</a>: Information on various BeStMan architectures
</li> <li> <a href="https://sdm.lbl.gov/bestman/" target="_top">Bestman home page</a>: Bestman project home
</li></ul> 
<p />
<p />
<h2 class="twikinetRoundedAttachments"><span class="twikinetHeader"><a name="Installation"></a> Installation </span></h2>
<p /> <ul>
<li> <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/Release3/InstallOSGBestmanSE" class="twikiLink">Install Bestman SE</a>: BeStMan installation interfacing with local disk
</li> <li> <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/Release3/InstallBestmanXrootdSE" class="twikiLink">Install Bestman Gateway Xrootd</a>: BeStMan gateway mode on top of XRootD
</li> <li> <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/Release3/InstallHadoopSE" class="twikiLink">Install Bestman Gateway Hadoop</a>: BeStMan gateway mode on top of Hadoop
</li> <li> <a href="https://sdm.lbl.gov/twiki/bin/view/Software/BeStMan/BeStManGuide/Configuration" target="_top">LBNL Configuration Reference</a>
</li></ul> 
<p />
<h2 class="twikinetRoundedAttachments"><span class="twikinetHeader"><a name="Operation"></a> Operation </span></h2>
<p /> <ul>
<li> <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/Release3/LbnlSrmClient" class="twikiLink">LBNL SRM Client</a>: SRM client provided with BeStMan
</li> <li> <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/Release3/SrmTester" class="twikiLink">BeStMan SRMTester</a>: Tester for BeStMan SRM instances
</li> <li> <a href="/bin/view/Storage/BestmanAdler32Checksum" class="twikiLink">BestmanAdler32Checksum</a>: Using Adler checksums with BeStMan
</li></ul> 
